# Keep the Docker build context small and the image clean.
# Without this, `COPY . .` drags node_modules (GBs), git history, build output,
# and — critically — any local .env (secrets) into the build layer.
**/node_modules
.git
.github
**/dist
**/build
**/.svelte-kit
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.pnpm-store
coverage
**/.env
**/.env.*
*.log
.DS_Store
/data-local
scratchpad
docs
**/*.md
